metadata.scriptContent: npm run docker:db:down && npm run docker:db && npm run db:reset && npm run seed
npm run db:migrate-up && npm run db:data-sync && node dist/src/main
if [ "$DB_USER" != "root" ]; then tsx scripts/clean.ts; else echo 'Cannot run reset as root'; fi
if [ "$DB_USER" != "root" ]; then prisma migrate reset --skip-seed -f; else echo 'Cannot run reset as root'; fi
npm run db:reset && npm run seed
npm run db:reset:dev && npm run db:data-migration:migrate && npm run db:data-sync
npm run db:migrate-dev -- --name 'initial version' && npm run db:migrate-up seed
rimraf ./dist && npm run build && nest start --entryFile ./src/data-migration/scripts/migrate

metadata.description: Ballerine is an open-source infrastructure for user identity and risk management. Compose verification processes for any vertical and geography using modular building blocks, components, and 3rd party integrations.

metadata.scriptContent: npm run build && for i in ./examples/sdk ./examples/standalone ./examples/standalone-future; do cp -R ./dist/ballerine-sdk.umd.cjs $i; done

vite build && aws s3 cp ./dist/ballerine-sdk.umd.cjs s3://blrn-cdn-prod/js/$npm_package_version/ballerine-sdk.umd.cjs && aws s3 cp ./dist/ballerine-sdk.umd.cjs.map s3://blrn-cdn-prod/js/$npm_package_version/ballerine-sdk.umd.cjs.map
vite build && npm version patch && npm publish && npm run deploy:cdn:cf
